  nodes:
  - id: start
    speakerID: lyra
    text: I've finally reached the truth
    nextNodeID: 1
    choices: []
    requiredFlags:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 9cc3d14b9dc651b4c8d197dcd5f6c5b9, type: 2}
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0bd4ea81fb4c46f4b95fd4140e9cab7d, type: 2}
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
  - id: 1
    speakerID: ghost1
    text: Really? You found out who was the murderous fiend? The one who tried to
      quiet my magnificent voice?
    nextNodeID: 
    choices:
    - text: No one murdered you... you suffered an accident, and died because of
        an allergy reaction
      nextNodeID: 2
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      endsDialogue: 0
    - text: They murdered you because they wanted your precious necklace
      nextNodeID: 
      addFlags: []
      requiredFlags: []
      endsDialogue: 0
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents: []
  - id: 2
    speakerID: ghost1
    text: "Oh? Is that so? All of these years I've hold on to these grudge against
      the world who silenced me, when I was the one who didn't listen to others...
      how... sad... \n\n\nThank you... Lyra, was it? Now, I'll finally be able to
      rest this voice... "
    nextNodeID: 
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: ed83ddcd1271f88408fb4efb562267a6, type: 2}
  - id: 3
    speakerID: ghost1
    text: "I knew it... that butler... he was always after me, envious of my voice,
      my wealth, my POWER... \n\nI'LL SHATTER THIS UNGRATEFUL WORLD WITH THE POWER
      OF MY VOICE... "
    nextNodeID: 
    choices: []
    requiredFlags: []
    onEnterFlags: []
    onEnterEvents:
    - {fileID: 11400000, guid: bbd47d83a4602724db2c4e969b3a2e83, type: 2}
